         Table 2 shows r<sup>2</sup> values for each Speck versus mass values from particles smaller than 1 micron,
         between 1 up to and including 2.5 microns, and 2.5 microns up to and including 10 microns respectively. Here
         we see that the correlation coefficients are similar for the latter two ranges.
      </div>
   </div>
